==English==
===Noun phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''power set''' (''plural'' '''power sets''')

#{{settheory}} The set of all [[subset]]s of a set.  Notation for a set ''S'': <math>\mathcal{P}(S)</math> ''or'' 2<sup>''S''</sup>
#:''The '''power set''' of {1, 2} is {Ø, {1}, {2}, {1,&nbsp;2}}''

